Well, I know a member of my local user group who would quite possibly wish
to incorporate caps into a security-enhanced Linux distribution he is
developing, especially in light of an easy upgrade path to a true fs-based
solution.
> Just MVHO.
Yes, my goals were just to completely develop the idea, and for people to
fully _understand_ the idea; it appears you understand it quite well, and
merely reject it on understandable grounds.  Which is fine, and I
appreciate your feedback. 
